@inherits LayoutComponentBase
@using Hexalith.FrontComposer.Shell.Components.Layout

@* The FrontComposer shell is fully framework-owned: it renders the skip links (#fc-main-content / #fc-nav),
   the role="main" landmark, the nav landmark, the left navigation from the domain's registered nav entries
   (AgentsFrontComposerRegistration), and the header account control. The Agents admin-setup UI therefore only
   composes its body through the shell and never re-declares skip links or landmarks (FC-A11Y). *@
<FrontComposerShell>@Body</FrontComposerShell>
